{"word":"H631 - אָסַר - ʼâçar - aw-sar' - Bind","slug":"H631","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָסַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâçar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-sar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E1;&#x05E8; - 'a&#x0302;sar</b> - <i>aw-sar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>yoke</i> or <i>hitch</i>; by analogy to <i>fasten</i> in any sense, to <i>join</i> battle: - bind, fast, gird, harness, hold, keep, make ready, order, prepare, prison (-er), put in bonds, set in array, tie."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4147\">H4147</a>, <a href=\"#/H4149\">H4149</a>, <a href=\"#/H4562\">H4562</a>, <a href=\"#/H612\">H612</a>, <a href=\"#/H615\">H615</a>, <a href=\"#/H616\">H616</a>, <a href=\"#/H617\">H617</a>, <a href=\"#/H632\">H632</a>, <a href=\"#/H634\">H634</a>, <a href=\"#/H635\">H635</a>"}]}